t_audio_report_issue::clip_card_10::goal: Madda odeeffannoo kennan gaafadhu: dhimmichi dursa yoom jalqabe?
t_audio_report_issue::title: Sagalee dhimmaa
t_audio_report_issue::clip_card_5::goals: Sagalee waan dhimmicharratti qabatamuu qabuu waraabi.
t_audio_report_issue::clip_card_1::goals: Sagaleekee fayyadami yookaan taatichi akka dhimmicha beeksisu godhi.
t_audio_report_issue::clip_card_6::goals: Madda ogeessaa gaafadhu: Akkamitti namooti biroon dhimmicha furuu gargaaru?
t_audio_report_issue::clip_card_18::goal: Gara fuulduraatti dhimmichaaf maal akka eegamu ofii keetii nutti himi.
t_audio_report_issue::clip_card_8::goals: Sagalee namoota dhimmicharratti hojjechaa jiranii waraabi.
t_audio_report_issue::clip_card_16::goal: Gaafadh: Waa'ee dhimmichaa maaltu godhamaa jira?
t_audio_report_issue::clip_card_12::goal: Akka qaamoti seenicha keessaa itti dhimmicha jijjiiruuf irratti hojjechaa jiran nutti himi.
t_audio_report_issue::clip_card_11::goal: Sagalee waan baayyee barbaachisaa waa'ee dhimmichaa waraabi.
t_audio_report_issue::clip_card_15::goal: Sagalee waan namootni waa'ee dhimmichaa gochaa jiranii waraabi.
t_audio_report_issue::text_card_0::text: Qajoojiin kun dhimma hawaasaa kan hawaasichaaf barbaachisaa ta'e akka gabaastuuf gargaara. Muraaleen eeraman waraabbiiwwan hangafaa kan ati dhimmicha ittiin adda baastuu fi ibsitu haammata. Waraabbwwan irra utaaluuf bilisa ta'i, yookaan akka barbaachisetti waraabbiiwwan biroo fayyadami. Dabalataan, Fedhiikee akka guutanitti gaaffilee eeraman fudhadhu.
t_audio_report_issue::clip_card_4::goals: Sagalee dhiibbaa dhimmichi namootarra geessisuu waraabi.
t_audio_report_issue::clip_card_17::goal: Sagalee akka qaamichi(oti) itti dhimmicha furaa jiruu waraabi.
t_audio_report_issue::clip_card_3::goals: Gaafadhu: dhimmichi akkamitti nama dhuunfaa yookaan hawaasicha tuqa?
t_audio_report_issue::clip_card_14::goal: Nama miidhame gaafadhu: dhimmichi akkamitti akka furamu barbaadda?
t_audio_report_issue::clip_card_9::goals: Waa'ee dhimmichaa haqoota hawwatoo ta'anii fi maaliif akka jalqabe nutti himi.
t_audio_report_issue::clip_card_13::goal: Sagalee nama warra miidhame quunnamaa jiruu waraabi.
